categories: Category:Plants of the Outer Rim Territories

nodes.text: A species of low-growing weed was found on the planet of Lok. During the Galactic Civil War, Ran Machado was ordered to remove the weeds from Nym's Stronghold by Nym, the leader of the Lok Revenants.

This low growing weed appeared in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
